cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Quetzal: per-gene Poisson NMF + genome-wide flashier factorisation of TCGA RNA splicing"
message: "If you use Quetzal, please cite this software."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Quinn
    family-names: Hauck
