repository-code: ""   # fill in once the GitHub URL exists
url: ""               # same
keywords:
  - alternative-splicing
  - rna-seq
  - tcga
  - leafcutter
  - poisson-nmf
  - matrix-factorization
  - flashier
abstract: >
  Quetzal builds a per-gene Poisson NMF over leafcutter junction counts
  for every gene in TCGA and lifts the resulting cohort-driving factors
  into a single genome-wide flashier factorisation. Output factors
  ("GSPs") recover known splicing factor disruption programs and
  highlight novel cohort-specific events.
